com.sociam.android.model

Class Tag

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sociam.android.model.Tag

  • public class Tag
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is a model of each tag. Tag is used for messaging system. Tag has 2 propaties and 2 settings,
    Propaties : one is category and another is name. for example, a tag has category 'general' and name 'female'
    Settings : one is usersettings which shows if the user sets this tag as defult, another is msg_setting which is used when the user sends a message
    Version:
    1
    Author:
    yukki
